column2: SELECT TOP # --P.SpecObjID as objid_P, S.SpecObjID as objid_S, --  P.subclass as class_P, S.subclass as class_S,   P.z as z_P, S.z as z_S,   N.distance FROM    SpecPhotoAll P			  -- P is the primary object   JOIN Neighbors N ON P.ObjID = N.ObjID  -- N is the neighbor link   JOIN	SpecPhotoAll S ON S.ObjID = N.NeighborObjID  -- S is a secondary galaxy nearby P WHERE    P.ObjID < S.ObjID                     -- avoid duplicates   and P.class = GALAXY&&&STARFORMING&&&STARBURST)   -- Make sure the primary is starforming/bursting
